div.p: Encode entire source sequence once. Cache encoder outputs for cross-attention.
Start generation with beginning-of-sequence token. Decoder attends to encoder outputs via cross-attention.
Project decoder output to vocabulary logits. Apply softmax to get probability distribution.
Select token with highest probability. No sampling, no beam searchpure greedy.
Append selected token to generated sequence. Feed extended sequence back to decoder.
Continue until end-of-sequence token or max length. Return final generated sequence.
